        <body>
                <p conref="carrier-grade-install-download.dita#topic7148cgid/intro"/>
                <p>Launch the <xref href="https://helion.hpwsportal.com/catalog.html#/Home/Show"
                        format="html" scope="external">Helion Distribution Network
                        (HDN)</xref>. You must <xref
                                href="https://idm.pod1.prod-core.hpwsportal.com/webid/"
                                format="html" scope="external">obtain a user account on HDN</xref>
                        in order to download these files. </p>
                <section>In a browser, navigate to <xref
                        href="https://helion.hpwsportal.com/catalog.html#/Home/Show"
                        format="html" scope="external">Helion Download Network(HDN)</xref>.
                        <ol id="ul_lvg_jb2_xs">
                                <li>Click <b>Sign In</b> to log in using your account. </li>
                                <li>After signing in, click the <b>Downloads</b> link in the menu on
                                        the left side of the page.</li>
                                <li>Click the <b>Downloads</b> tab and locate the following
                                        download. </li>
                        </ol><ul id="ul_zll_rjv_g5">
                                <li><b>Helion Carrier Grade 2.0.0 VRS</b> Installation files for the
                                        HP Helion OpenStack Carrier Grade Tahoe, Memphis, and
                                        Sacramento deployments. This link will download the
                                        <codeph>hcg2_kvm_esx_ironic_vrs.tar.gz</codeph>
                                        file. </li>
                                <li><b>Helion Carrier Grade 2.0 VRS Checksum</b>. The SHA256
                                        checksum for Helion Carrier Grade 2.0 VRS. This link will
                                        download the
                                        <codeph>hcg2_kvm_esx_ironic_vrs.tar.gz.sha256</codeph>
                                        file.</li>
                                <li><b>Helion Carrier Grade 2.0 VRS Signature</b>. The signature
                                        file for Helion Carrier Grade 2.0 VRS. This link will
                                        download the
                                        <codeph>hcg2_kvm_esx_ironic_vrs.tar.gz.sig</codeph>
                                        file.</li>
                        </ul><p><b>Note:</b> When downloading installation files, always download
                                and verify the signature file before installing. </p></section>
